#%RAML 1.0 DocumentationItem
title: Overview
content: |
  The System Observability Logs API provides a canonical contract for retrieving
  normalised logs across ELK, Splunk, Datadog, and Azure Monitor.

  This specification inherits shared governance assets from:
  - mule-utility-template-spec (template baseline)
  - mule-utility-common-fragment (shared security/traits/resource types)

  Vendor-specific response formats are intentionally hidden behind the canonical
  response model to keep downstream contracts stable.
